                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160710-83-off438 t18160710-83-cd439"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18160710-83-victim611" type="victimName">
                        Robert 
                        Adamson
                     <interp inst="t18160710-83-victim611" type="surname" value="Adamson"></interp>
