                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160710-83-defend610 t18160710-83-punish442"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
